text: Le Mesnil-Auzouf is a former commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2017, it was merged into the new commune of Dialan sur Chaîne.Arrêté préfectoral 26 September 2016 == References == Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Le Mesnil-Auzouf
